libgedit-gtksourceview: libgedit-gtksourceview (Source code editing widget)
libgedit-gtksourceview:
libgedit-gtksourceview: libgedit-gtksourceview is a library that extends GtkTextView,
libgedit-gtksourceview: the standard GTK widget for multiline text editing. This library
libgedit-gtksourceview: adds support for syntax highlighting, undo/redo, file loading and
libgedit-gtksourceview: saving, search and replace, a completion system, printing, displaying
libgedit-gtksourceview: line numbers, and other features typical of a source code editor.
libgedit-gtksourceview:
libgedit-gtksourceview: homepage: https://github.com/gedit-technology/libgedit-gtksourceview
